name: XDoge
description: Welcome to XDoge! A fusion of X and everyone's favorite meme, DOGE! XDoge is a 1% tax token of which each transaction on the blockchain feeds the liquidity pool and adds marketing funds for further development and marketing activation for the project. All tokens were added to Uniswap V2 liquidity pool and the pool was sent to the burn address, hence no one has access to the LP. The contract is also renounced and no functions can be called for any sort of revision.
